modName: Floki preset from the Vikings TV Series
summary: I made a preset for Floki from the Vikings TV Series
descriptionHtml:
This is the first preset I am uploading, hopefully I've done everything right in terms of giving credit and those things.

I used following mods to create this preset: (Guess you need them, too)

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29977/?]XCE - Warpaint and Dirt by [b]Xenius[/b] [/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes Of Beauty by [b]Gabriel Mailhot as LogRaam[/b] [/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52322/?]WSCO - Windsong Skyrim Character Overhaul by [b]Windsong[/b] [/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu by [b]Expired[/b] 

[/url]Installation:

Download the archive and put the file inside to your Skyrim folder:
D:\program files (x86)\steam\steamapps\common\Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets


Also take a look at my Ragnar Lodbrok preset:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/79315/?]Ragnar Lodbrok preset from the Vikings TV Series[/url]
author: Dennis Olafson
